"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The Ukrainian president is attending a Nato meeting in Turkey. He plans to ask for more interceptor missiles to help his country.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukrainian President at Nato Meeting\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania est\u00e1 en una reuni\u00f3n de la OTAN en Turqu\u00eda. \u00c9l planea pedir m\u00e1s misiles para ayudar a su pa\u00eds.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de Ucrania en reuni\u00f3n de la OTAN\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Former prisoners are accusing some men of abuse in detention centers. They want these men to be put on trial for their actions.\",            \"english_title\": \"Abuse Accusations by Former Prisoners\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ex prisioneros est\u00e1n acusando a algunos hombres de abuso en centros de detenci\u00f3n. Quieren que estos hombres sean juzgados por sus acciones.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acusaciones de abuso por ex prisioneros\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Tehran, there were three days of public mourning. Iran's leaders wanted the world to see this political event.\",            \"english_title\": \"Public Mourning in Tehran\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Teher\u00e1n, hubo tres d\u00edas de luto p\u00fablico. Los l\u00edderes de Ir\u00e1n quer\u00edan que el mundo viera este evento pol\u00edtico.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Luto p\u00fablico en Teher\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"South African police are looking into a case of attempted murder. So far, no one has been arrested.\",            \"english_title\": \"Attempted Murder Investigation in South Africa\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda de Sud\u00e1frica est\u00e1 investigando un caso de intento de asesinato. Hasta ahora, nadie ha sido arrestado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Investigaci\u00f3n de intento de asesinato en Sud\u00e1frica\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two former Syrian officials are on trial in Vienna, Austria. They are accused of committing crimes against people who opposed the former Syrian leader Bashar al-Assad.\",            \"english_title\": \"Syrian Officials on Trial in Austria\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos ex funcionarios sirios est\u00e1n en juicio en Viena, Austria. Est\u00e1n acusados de cometer cr\u00edmenes contra personas que se opusieron al ex l\u00edder sirio Bashar al-Assad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Funcionarios sirios en juicio en Austria\"        }    ]}"